<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Inn ah ra tlung, Nangmah cu na ba ko, Lam kha a muih ca-ah, Na re a
 thei ko cang, Maw a tlaumi fa, Inn ah ra tlung tuah,

[C1]
   Inn ah ra tlung cang tuah. 2.Inn ah ra tlung, Nangmah kan in hngak
   ko, Zanlei khuamui zongah, Hauka in kan in hngak, Maw a tlaumi fa, Inn ah
   ra tlung tuah.

[V2]
 Inn ah ra tlung, ngaihchiat harnak chungin, Sual le ningzahnak le,
 Tukforhtu kut chungin. Maw a tlaumi fa, Inn ah ra tlung tuah.

[C2]
   Inn ah ra tlung cang tuah. 2.Inn ah ra tlung, Nangmah kan in hngak
   ko, Zanlei khuamui zongah, Hauka in kan in hngak, Maw a tlaumi fa, Inn ah
   ra tlung tuah.

[V3]
 Inn ah ra tlung, Rawl tampi a um ko, Lawmhnak in donnak le, Hawikom he
 tonnak zong, Maw a tlaumi fa, Inn ah ra tlung tuah.

[C3]
   Inn ah ra tlung cang tuah. 2.Inn ah ra tlung, Nangmah kan in hngak
   ko, Zanlei khuamui zongah, Hauka in kan in hngak, Maw a tlaumi fa, Inn ah
   ra tlung tuah.</lyrics>
